{"tid":2152704,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"一曝光就被酸「足球隊是為了談戀愛」　Apink夏榮宣布退出…TWICE志效、Mina跟進：別讓粉絲誤會","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2f081a428c70965795692737514af630a8eb1f4a","tid":2152704,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"南韓民眾對足球的熱愛處處可見，不只各地區會自組球隊，有些大型公司行號也會舉辦社內的足球賽，男藝人們也有組成明星足球隊每週一起運動幾次，明星女子足球隊「FC Rumor」7月也誕生，怎料卻成了酸民的眼中釘，不管怎麼解釋最後仍敵不過輿論，其中幾名女偶像都已經退出了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5067/d5067308.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5067%2Fd5067308.jpg&h=2753e47d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n.▲吳夏榮曾上傳FC Rumor合照。（圖／翻攝自吳夏榮IG）<br />\n<br />\nApink成員吳夏榮11日開直播和粉絲宣布退出FC Rumor，談到原本只是因為有趣才會聚在一起，但消息曝光後迎來的卻是很多的臆測和反對留言，雖然曾寫下長文澄清但流言並沒有消退，想過很多的辦法卻又害怕會造成反效果，畢竟團內不只有藝人還有一般人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5067/d5067309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5067%2Fd5067309.jpg&h=ebf9e4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼吳夏榮曾對外解釋「只是喜歡足球而聚在一起」。（圖／翻攝自吳夏榮IG、推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5067/5067331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5067%2F5067331.jpg&h=56d92315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因此，吳夏榮選擇退出團隊並透露TWICE志效和Mina也都退出了：「怕會因為這個聚會讓粉絲難過，因為惡意猜測讓身邊的人受傷難過，所以選擇退出。」而她也曾看過粉絲說「希望就退出吧」，所以雖然抱持著的心態很單純正面，但也無法忽視可能迎來的問題以及對他人造成的傷害。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5067/d5067327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5067%2Fd5067327.jpg&h=d085de57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE Mina和志效也退出FC Rumor。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，吳夏榮退出FC Rumor已經好一段時間了，她表示在一有爭議的時候就選擇退出：「和已退出的朋友們討論說，如果我們真的想踢就低調一點，不要對外宣布，就我們之間去借場地也可以，想正式上課的話去學就可以了，然後不要讓粉絲誤會，就這樣選擇退出。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMINA同志效都有男朋友。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812ab3d368603e8eb257500eb439f88e2e1fb5e2","tid":2152704,"uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"咁令女唔媾仔唔通留對手畀你班毒撚握咩"},{"pid":"a81947189c55b2dc0a0f91fb7aa193405db884df","tid":2152704,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"唔係第二個mina咩"},{"pid":"246d52faef951c73b6cf6d8ac89f6ead63754bc5","tid":2152704,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"812ab3d368603e8eb257500eb439f88e2e1fb5e2","tid":2152704,"uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"咁令女唔媾仔唔通留對手畀你班毒撚握咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DwoSDK4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwoSDK4.gif&h=d275187d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"804588ab1c65b2c04c9a3747567b92abfab33312","tid":2152704,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a81947189c55b2dc0a0f91fb7aa193405db884df","tid":2152704,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"唔係第二個mina咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"唔清楚"},{"pid":"3f49c382d790b821125b991ff8141ef5911e13c0","tid":2152704,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"我守住定延個龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10d3bc16f5112dcb85a609046fafc23ef07a2e1","tid":2152704,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f49c382d790b821125b991ff8141ef5911e13c0","tid":2152704,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"我守住定延個龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:50:13.000Z","msg":"頂入佢肛門"},{"pid":"4d017165257f5f83f4d3910678c2b881